{"tid":680963,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"梁 芷 珊 增 磅　襯 高 大 法 籍 男 友","createTime":"2018-05-27T15:13:55.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-27T23:51:34.000Z","uid":35964,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"5374ef09fadfea420d78c465dd3733d71ff9a2da","tid":680963,"uid":35964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T15:13:55.000Z","msg":"現年49歲的梁芷珊跟羅傑承結束15年婚姻，去年回復單身後，覓得第二春，與法籍三星米芝蓮廚師Olivier墮愛河，日前兩人拍拖到跑馬地嘆糖水，之前因陷婚變暴瘦的梁芷珊，在新戀情滋潤下體重有增，不再瘦骨嶙峋。<br />\n<br />\n初時避忌<br />\n當日約傍晚5時許，本報記者在跑馬地一間糖水舖發現梁芷珊，而廚師男友Olivier則在店門外傾電話，之後他返入糖水舖跟梁芷珊埋單離去，初時兩人似有避忌，行到一前一後相隔約五個身位，途經一間賣洋酒的舖頭時，兩人才站在一齊window shopping，只見他們在門外手指指，最終都沒有入內幫襯，之後兩人就縮短距離，齊齊行去街市附近取車。<br />\n<br />\n齊返香閨<br />\n約6呎高的Olivier高大威猛，雖然梁芷珊着了4吋高踭鞋，但站在男友身邊仍然似小鳥依人，雖然身形增磅不再骨瘦如柴，惟面色依然發黑，但就精神奕奕，明顯沐浴在愛河之中，之後就由男友做柴可夫直駛梁芷珊位於大坑的香閨。<br />\n<br />\n曾任填詞人、作家、編劇的才女梁芷珊，與前夫羅傑承育有15歲女兒，兩人表示離婚不涉第三者，梁芷珊回復單身後被Olivier狂追，囡囡都贊成媽咪發展新戀情。日前梁芷珊在社交網罕晒男友合照，不過男友卻做了「影後」，兩人蜜遊台北在松山慈佑宮留影，又去嘆日本菜食至愛海膽，網民都留言讚她：「變回以前那樣漂亮」、「容光煥發」、「笑得好甜」。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24ec3p2a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24ec3p2a.jpg&h=45fae4c1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24ec3p3a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24ec3p3a.jpg&h=5281f082&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24ec3p1a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24ec3p1a.jpg&h=7c77d804&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180524/large/24ec3p4a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180524%2Flarge%2F24ec3p4a.jpg&h=36e09d4b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"289223aca509b3d439d5ac3d0399f8960bff517c","tid":680963,"uid":9812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T16:02:30.000Z","msg":"成日覺得佢係有病"},{"pid":"5bf74a58e2be58f225a52fb0469a8057e37a6464","tid":680963,"uid":81569,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:01:24.000Z","msg":"屌我以前成日分唔到佢同林淑敏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n但呢家睇真d 大小姐靚十萬倍"},{"pid":"0d687dd5169ef2cf70381b54f83cbbd3ce50ffa0","tid":680963,"uid":43575,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"好大分別喎<br />\n，前夫係咪剋薄佢？"},{"pid":"0de1e2f328b7d73f79d7b0c16b27e749c6bd148d","tid":680963,"uid":41477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T22:56:42.000Z","msg":"以前塊面黑晒好似有病"},{"pid":"972f6b600fb9d02299abc541f24faabe3528abf5","tid":680963,"uid":23140,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-27T23:51:34.000Z","msg":"竟然唔係潘頓"}]}